{
  "stem": "8916.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother mostly was to happy to see me and mad that it happened to me, you know, I mean, just two together.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So those are kind of incidences I-- we went through.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was constant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- there was always that-- life in the ghetto was-- the worst part was, for one thing, we didn't have enough food.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The other was this insecurity, constant danger of being shot or getting into some kind of trouble.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of the time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of the time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, my father got this-- a job across the street from where he used to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was this factory where he did some work prior to the invasion.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when the Germans came in, of course they confiscated all these factories and he lost his job.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that factory across the street was taken over by a German officer, who came to Krakow and came to Poland, as so many did, to seek their fortunes, because it was a-- quite a lucrative thing to do for these Germans to come into a newly-occupied land.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this particular person was a German officer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was a-- in the counterintelligence.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he served the German army and the German-- the Nazis well, so he deserved the-- to be given this factory.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oskar Schindler.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He took over a company called Emalia, where they made pots and pans before the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And since he heard of my father and that he didn't have a job in the-- in his own place, and so Schindler hired him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so as a result, my father ended up to be one of the first Jews that Schindler hired.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, certainly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I met Schindler quite a-- quite a few times.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
